ruirea Gutenberg','If you want to learn more about how to build additional blocks, or if you are interested in helping with the project, head over to the <a href="%s">GitHub repository</a>.'=>'DacƒГ vrei sƒГ afli mai multe despre cum sƒГ construie»Щti blocuri suplimentare sau dacƒГ e»Щti interesat sƒГ aju»Ыi proiectul, mergi la <a href="%s">depozitarul GitHub</a>.','The WordPress community'=>'Comunitatea WordPress','Code is Poetry'=>'Codul este poezie','You can build any block you like, static or dynamic, decorative or plain. Here&#8217;s a quote block:'=>'Po»Ыi sƒГ construie»Щti orice bloc vrei, static sau dinamic, decorativ sau simplu. IatƒГ un bloc Citat:','Any block can opt into these alignments. The embed block has them also, and is responsive out of the box:'=>'Toate blocurile pot folosi aceste alinieri. Blocul de √Ѓnglobare le are, de asemenea, »Щi este gata de func»Ыionare:','The above is a gallery with just two images. It&#8217;s an easier way to create visually appealing layouts, without having to deal with floats. You can also easily convert the gallery back to individual images again, by using the block switcher.'=>'Mai sus este o galerie cu doar douƒГ imagini. Este o modalitate mai u»ЩoarƒГ de a crea aranjamente atrƒГgƒГtoare din punct de vedere vizual, fƒГrƒГ nicio problemƒГ. De asemenea, po»Ыi converti u»Щor galeria √Ѓnapoi la imagini individuale, folosind comutatorul pentru blocuri.','Sure, the full-wide image can be pretty big. But sometimes the image is worth it.'=>'Desigur, imaginea √Ѓn lƒГ»Ыime completƒГ poate fi destul de mare. Dar uneori imaginea meritƒГ.','Accessibility is important &mdash; don&#8217;t forget image alt attribute'=>'Accesibilitatea este importantƒГ &mdash; nu uita de atributul alternativƒГ imagine','If you combine the new <strong>wide</strong> and <strong>full-wide</strong> alignments with galleries, you can create a very media rich layout, very quickly:'=>'DacƒГ combini noile alinieri <strong>mare</strong> »Щi <strong>lƒГ»Ыime completƒГ</strong> cu galeriile, po»Ыi crea un aranjament cu foarte multe elemente media, foarte repede:','Media Rich'=>'MultƒГ media','You can change the amount of columns in your galleries by dragging a slider in the block inspector in the sidebar.'=>'Po»Ыi modifica numƒГrul de coloane din galerii prin tragerea unui carusel √Ѓn inspectorul de blocuri din bara lateralƒГ.','Blocks can be anything you need. For instance, you may want to add a subdued quote as part of the composition of your text, or you may prefer to display a giant stylized one. All of these options are available in the inserter.'=>'Blocurile pot face orice ai nevoie. De exemplu, poate vrei sƒГ adaugi un citat discret √Ѓn con»Ыinutul textului sau poate preferi sƒГ afi»Щezi unul cu litere uria»Щe. Toate aceste op»Ыiuni sunt disponibile √Ѓn dispozitivul de inserare.','The information corresponding to the source of the quote is a separate text field, similar to captions under images, so the structure of the quote is protected even if you select, modify, or remove the source. It&#8217;s always easy to add it back.'=>'Informa»Ыiile corespunzƒГtoare sursei citatului sunt √Ѓntr-un c√Ґmp de text separat, similar cu textele asociate de sub imagini, astfel structura citatului este protejatƒГ chiar dacƒГ selectezi, modifici sau √ЃnlƒГturi sursa. Este mereu u»Щor sƒГ-l adaugi √Ѓnapoi.','Matt Mullenweg, 2017'=>'Matt Mullenweg, 2017','The editor will endeavor to create a new page and post building experience that makes writing rich posts effortless, and has вАЬblocksвАЭ to make it easy what today might take shortcodes, custom HTML, or вАЬmystery meatвАЭ embed discovery.'=>'Editorul se va strƒГdui sƒГ creeze o nouƒГ experien»ЫƒГ √Ѓn construirea articolelor »Щi paginilor care sƒГ facƒГ facilƒГ scrierea unor articole bogate »Щi are вАЮblocuriвАЭ care sƒГ u»Щureze ceea ce fac astƒГzi scurt-codurile, HTML-ul personalizat »Щi altele.','A huge benefit of blocks is that you can edit them in place and manipulate your content directly. Instead of having fields for editing things like the source of a quote, or the text of a button, you can directly change the content. Try editing the following quote:'=>'Un avantaj imens al blocurilor este cƒГ le po»Ыi edita pe loc »Щi sƒГ-»Ыi gestionezi direct con»Ыinutul. √Оn loc sƒГ ai c√Ґmpuri pentru editarea elementelor, cum ar fi sursa unui citat sau textul unui buton, po»Ыi schimba direct con»Ыinutul. √ОncearcƒГ editarea citatului urmƒГtor:','Visual Editing'=>'Editare vizualƒГ','And <em>Lists</em> like this one of course :)'=>'»Шi <em>liste</em> ca aceasta, bine√Ѓn»Ыeles :)','Layout blocks, like Buttons, Hero Images, Separators, etc.'=>'Blocuri de aspect, cum ar fi butoane, imagini Hero, separatori etc.','Embeds, like YouTube, Tweets, or other WordPress posts.'=>'√ОnglobƒГri, cum ar fi YouTube, twituri sau alte articole WordPress.','Galleries'=>'Galerii','Images &amp; Videos'=>'Imagini »Щi videouri','Text &amp; Headings'=>'Text »Щi subtitluri','Go give it a try, you may discover things WordPress can already add into your posts that you didn&#8217;t know about. Here&#8217;s a short list of what you can currently find there:'=>'√ОncearcƒГ-l, po»Ыi descoperi unele lucruri pe care WordPress poate le-a adƒГugat deja √Ѓn articolele tale, de care nu »Щtiai. IatƒГ o scurtƒГ listƒГ cu ceea ce po»Ыi gƒГsi √Ѓn prezent:','Imagine everything that WordPress can do is available to you quickly and in the same place on the interface. No need to figure out HTML tags, classes, or remember complicated shortcode syntax. That&#8217;s the spirit behind the inserterвАФthe <code>(+)</code> button you&#8217;ll see around the editorвАФwhich allows you to browse all available content blocks and add them into your post. Plugins and themes are able to register their own, opening up all sort of possibilities for rich editing and publishing.'=>'ImagineazƒГ-»Ыi cƒГ tot ceea ce poate face WordPress este disponibil rapid »Щi √Ѓn acela»Щi loc, pe o interfa»ЫƒГ. Nu trebuie sƒГ ai cuno»Щtin»Ыe despre taguri HTML, clase sau sƒГ-»Ыi aminte»Щti sintaxa complicatƒГ a scurt-codurilor. Acesta este spiritul din spatele √ЃnserƒГrilor - butonul <code>(+)</code> pe care √Ѓl vei vedea peste tot √Ѓn editor - care √Ѓ»Ыi permite sƒГ rƒГsfoie»Щti toate blocurile de con»Ыinut disponibile »Щi sƒГ le adaugi √Ѓn articolul tƒГu. Modulele »Щi temele pot sƒГ-»Щi √Ѓnregistreze propriile lor blocuri, deschiz√Ґnd tot felul de posibilitƒГ»Ыi pentru editare, redactare »Щi publicare.','The <em>Inserter</em> Tool'=>'Instrumentul <em>InserƒГri</em>','Try selecting and removing or editing the caption, now you don&#8217;t have to be careful about selecting the image or other text by mistake and ruining the presentation.'=>'√ОncearcƒГ selectarea »Щi √ЃnlƒГturarea sau editarea textului asociat, acum nu trebuie sƒГ fii foarte atent dacƒГ selectezi o imagine sau un alt text din gre»ЩealƒГ pentru cƒГ nu strici prezentarea.','If your theme supports it, you&#8217;ll see the "wide" button on the image toolbar. Give it a try.'=>'DacƒГ tema ta √Ѓl suportƒГ, vei vedea butonul вАЮmareвАЭ √Ѓn bara de unelte pentru imagini. √ОncearcƒГ-l.','Handling images and media with the utmost care is a primary focus of the new editor. Hopefully, you&#8217;ll find aspects of adding captions or going full-width with your pictures much easier and robust than before.'=>'Gestionarea cu maximƒГ aten»Ыie a imaginilor »Щi elementelor media este punctul central al noului editor. SperƒГm cƒГ toate aspectele legate de adƒГugarea de texte asociate sau de lƒГ»Ыimea completƒГ a imaginilor √Ѓ»Ыi vor pƒГrea mult mai u»Щoare »Щi mai robuste dec√Ґt √Ѓnainte.','A Picture is Worth a Thousand Words'=>'O fotografie valoreazƒГ mai mult dec√Ґt o mie de cuvinte','Headings are separate blocks as well, which helps with the outline and organization of your content.'=>'Subtitlurile sunt »Щi ele blocuri separate, care te ajutƒГ la conturarea »Щi organizarea con»Ыinutului.','... like this one, which is right aligned.'=>'... ca acesta, care este aliniat corect.','What you are reading now is a <strong>text block</strong> the most basic block of all. The text block has its own controls to be moved freely around the post...'=>'Ceea ce cite»Щti acum este un <strong>bloc text</strong>, care este blocul de bazƒГ. Blocul text are comenzi proprii pentru a fi mutat fƒГrƒГ nicio restric»Ыie oriunde √Ѓn articol.','The goal of this new editor is to make adding rich content to WordPress simple and enjoyable. This whole post is composed of <em>pieces of content</em>вАФsomewhat similar to LEGO bricksвАФthat you can move around and interact with. Move your cursor around and you&#8217;ll notice the different blocks light up with outlines and arrows. Press the arrows to reposition blocks quickly, without fearing about losing things in the process of copying and pasting.'=>'Scopul acestui editor nou este de a face mai simplƒГ »Щi mai plƒГcutƒГ adƒГugarea unui con»Ыinut bogat √Ѓn WordPress. Acest articol este compus √Ѓn totalitate din <em>bucƒГ»Ыi de con»Ыinut</em> - ceva similar cu piesele LEGO - pe care le po»Ыi muta »Щi totodatƒГ sƒГ interac»Ыionezi cu ele. MutƒГ cursorul √Ѓn toate pƒГr»Ыile »Щi vei observa cƒГ diferite blocuri se lumineazƒГ cu contururi »Щi sƒГge»Ыi. ApasƒГ pe sƒГge»Ыi pentru a repozi»Ыiona rapid blocurile, fƒГrƒГ teamƒГ cƒГ pierzi lucruri √Ѓn procesul de copiere »Щi plasare.','Of Mountains &amp; Printing Presses'=>'De mun»Ыi »Щi prese de tipƒГrire','Welcome to the Gutenberg Editor'=>'Bine ai venit la editorul Gutenberg','Learn more'=>'√Оnva»ЫƒГ mai multe','Small'=>'Mic','https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/gutenberg/'=>'https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/gutenberg/','Support'=>'Suport','No comments to show.'=>'Niciun comentariu de arƒГtat.','%1$s on %2$s'=>'%1$s pe %2$s','Select Post'=>'SelecteazƒГ articolul','Select Week'=>'SelecteazƒГ sƒГptƒГm√Ґna','Select Day'=>'SelecteazƒГ ziua','Select Month'=>'SelecteazƒГ luna','Select Year'=>'SelecteazƒГ anul','Archives'=>'Arhive','Large'=>'Mare','block descriptionAdd a block that displays content pulled from other sites, like Twitter or YouTube.'=>'AdaugƒГ un bloc care afi»ЩeazƒГ con»Ыinut extras de pe alte site-uri, cum ar fi Twitter sau YouTube.','Pagination'=>'Pagina»Ыie','Block'=>'Bloc' . "\0" . '%d blocuri' . "\0" . '%d de blocuri','Table of Contents'=>'Cuprins','(no title)'=>'(fƒГrƒГ titlu)','Close'=>'√Оnchide','Read more'=>'Cite»Щte mai mult','Experiments'=>'Experimente','Edit'=>'EditeazƒГ','Gutenberg development mode requires files to be built. Run <code>npm install</code> to install dependencies, <code>npm run build</code> to build the files or <code>npm run dev</code> to build the files and watch for changes. Read the <a href="https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/blob/HEAD/docs/contributors/code/getting-started-with-code-contribution.md">contributing</a> file for more information.'=>'Modul de dezvoltare Gutenberg necesitƒГ sƒГ fie construite fi»Щiere. RuleazƒГ <code>npm install</code> pentru a instala dependen»Ыe, <code>npm run build</code> pentru a construi fi»Щierele sau <code>npm run dev</code> pentru a construi fi»Щierele »Щi pentru a urmƒГri modificƒГrile. Pentru mai multe informa»Ыii, cite»Щte fi»Щierul <a href="https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/blob/HEAD/docs/contributors/code/getting-started-with-code-contribution.md">contribuie</a>.','Gutenberg Team'=>'Echipa Gutenberg','https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg'=>'https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg','Gutenberg'=>'Gutenberg','%s ago'=>'Acum %s','%s from now'=>'%s de acum','Gutenberg requires WordPress %s or later to function properly. Please upgrade WordPress before activating Gutenberg.'=>'Pentru a func»Ыiona corect, Gutenberg necesitƒГ WordPress %s sau o versiune ulterioarƒГ. Te rog actualizeazƒГ WordPress √Ѓnainte de a activa Gutenberg.','Documentation'=>'Documenta»Ыie','Demo'=>'Demonstra»Ыie']];